pos_mean_info_list.mean: 使看法深入内心；使成内景

word_mean_info__list.difference: 指某物的内部，尤指某物的内侧；也可指内地的或国内的。
指朝着中心或内部方向的，侧重方向而不是位置；也可指内心的隐密活动。
含义广泛，指事物中心或接近中心的部位，也可指内心隐密的活动。
多指处于某物内部或靠近内部，常可与inner换用，可引申指内幕的，秘密的。
书面用词，医学上多用，指事物的内部，也可指国内的或内政的。

word_group.brief_definition: 室内设计师；内饰设计师；室内装饰设计师

bilingual.source: The boat's interior is lined with teak.
bilingual.target: 这艘船的内部用柚木装饰。

bilingual.source: The interior of the space capsule is very cramped.
bilingual.target: 太空舱的内部非常狭小。

bilingual.source: The interior of the house was beautifully decorated.
bilingual.target: 房子的内部装饰得非常漂亮。

bilingual.source: The interior of the restaurant was cozy and inviting.
bilingual.target: 餐厅的内部温馨而有吸引力。

bilingual.source: She spent hours cleaning the interior of her car.
bilingual.target: 她花了好几个小时清洁她车的内部。

bilingual.source: The new restaurant has a very stylish interior design.
bilingual.target: 这家新餐厅的内部设计非常时尚。

bilingual.source: The owners of the restaurant decided to renovate the interior.
bilingual.target: 餐厅的所有者决定翻新内部。

bilingual.source: The new restaurant in town has a very sny interior.
bilingual.target: 镇上的新餐厅有一个非常时髦的内部装饰。

bilingual.source: The cabin's woody interior made it feel cozy and comfortable.
bilingual.target: 小屋的木质的内部让人感觉温馨舒适。

bilingual.source: Scientists study moonquake to understand the moon's interior.
bilingual.target: 科学家研究月震以了解月球的内部结构。

yingyinNormal.en: Unit cell contains two carbon atoms. Interior angle of a hexagon is 120 degrees.
yingyinNormal.zh: 单元晶格包涵了两个碳原子，六边形的内角为120°。

yingyinNormal.en: If you fall in, you can't send signals back out. Light can't get out from the interior.
yingyinNormal.zh: 如果你掉进去，你就无法将信号发回来。光无法从里面发射出来。

yingyinNormal.en: China's large interior allows for engineering projects to be rolled out on a grand scale.
yingyinNormal.zh: 中国广袤的内陆使得诸多工程项目得以开展实施，而且体量巨大。

yingyinNormal.en: Spend some time in the Big Island's interior and explore the Hawaii Volcanoes National Park.
yingyinNormal.zh: 花些时间深入大岛的内陆，并探索夏威夷火山国家公园。

yingyinNormal.en: You should now have one crusty loaf with a soft interior or crumb, airy and light but satisfyingly chewy.
yingyinNormal.zh: 现在面包外面很脆，里面很松软，多孔很轻，但是嚼劲正好。
